Paper: hep-th/9801012

Date: 1998-01-05

Title: Dirac electron in a Coulomb Field in 2+1 Dimensions

Authors: V.R. Khalilov and Choon-Lin Ho

Comments: 11 pages, RevTex

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A13 (1998) 615-622

Exact solutions of Dirac equation in two spatial dimensions in the Coulombfield are obtained. Equation which determines the so-called critical charge ofthe Coulomb field is derived and solved for a simple model.